question_text: As you may know, there will be a presidential election on Nov. 8. Which one of the following candidates would you be most likely to support on Election Day?

Thinking about the presidential election, if the election for president were held today and the candidates were -- Democrats Hillary Clinton and Tim Kaine, Republicans Donald Trump and Mike Pence, Green Party candidates Jill Stein and Ajamu Baraka, Libertarian Party candidates Gary Johnson and Bill Weld, and Peace and Freedom Party candidates Gloria Estela la Riva and Dennis Banks, for whom would you vote?
